@startuml
title kEmber 输入到输出流水线时序图
caption 从场景导入、量化、局部求解到结果导出的主执行路径

autonumber
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultTextAlignment left
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20
skinparam BoxPadding 10

actor "调用方" as User
participant "应用入口\nsrc/application/" as AppEntry
database "输入场景" as InputScene
participant "场景导入与量化" as SceneImport
participant "布尔引擎\nsrc/core/" as BooleanEngine
participant "任务运行时" as Runtime
participant "空间细分" as Subdivision
participant "参考点传播" as ReferencePropagation
participant "叶子局部求解" as LeafSolver
participant "局部 BSP / Arrangement" as LocalArrangement
participant "面分类与布尔判定" as FaceClassification
participant "结果组装" as ResultAssembly
participant "结果导出" as SceneExport
database "输出结果" as OutputScene

User -> AppEntry : 提交输入网格与布尔表达
AppEntry -> InputScene : 读取场景数据
InputScene --> AppEntry : 原始网格 / 配置

AppEntry -> SceneImport : 导入并量化
activate SceneImport
SceneImport -> SceneImport : 坐标缩放与整数化
SceneImport --> AppEntry : 输入 polygon soup
deactivate SceneImport

note over SceneImport,BooleanEngine
从量化后的整数 polygon soup 开始，
内部流程进入 EMBER 的精确整数域。
end note

AppEntry -> BooleanEngine : 创建并启动布尔作业
activate BooleanEngine
BooleanEngine -> Runtime : 建立任务上下文
BooleanEngine -> Subdivision : 启动顶层子问题

loop 直到所有子问题处理完成
  activate Subdivision
  Subdivision -> Subdivision : AABB 分割与 early-out 检查

  alt 到达叶子子问题
    Subdivision -> ReferencePropagation : 准备局部 reference / WNV
    activate ReferencePropagation
    ReferencePropagation --> LeafSolver : 叶子子问题 + 局部状态
    deactivate ReferencePropagation

    activate LeafSolver
    LeafSolver -> LocalArrangement : 构建局部 BSP / arrangement
    activate LocalArrangement
    LocalArrangement --> LeafSolver : 互不重叠局部面
    deactivate LocalArrangement

    LeafSolver -> FaceClassification : segment tracing 与 WNV 判定
    activate FaceClassification
    FaceClassification --> BooleanEngine : 分类后的输出面
    deactivate FaceClassification
    deactivate LeafSolver
  else 继续细分
    Subdivision -> Runtime : 派发新的子问题
    Runtime -> Subdivision : 调度下一个子问题
  end

  deactivate Subdivision
end

note over Subdivision,FaceClassification
叶子阶段只处理局部子问题，
避免先构建全局 arrangement 或全局加速结构。
end note

BooleanEngine -> ResultAssembly : 汇总并组装全部输出面
activate ResultAssembly

opt 需要拓扑恢复或统一朝向
  ResultAssembly -> ResultAssembly : 恢复 mesh 拓扑 / 修正朝向
end

ResultAssembly -> SceneExport : 导出结果曲面与调试数据
deactivate ResultAssembly

activate SceneExport
SceneExport -> OutputScene : 写出文件 / 调试产物
SceneExport --> AppEntry : 返回执行结果
deactivate SceneExport

AppEntry --> User : 返回结果位置与运行状态
deactivate BooleanEngine

@enduml
